These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: aquamarine, white, emerald, pink, purple, lavender, amber
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, classical, jazz, r&b, reggae, rock, soul
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: climbing, golf, parkour, surfing, tennis, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the fan of classical and the fan of blues##2
 4. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the fan of r&b is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who likes purple##2
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person who likes amber is the fan of jazz##1
11. the fan of rock is the person who likes pink##1
12. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
13. the person who's sport is climbing is the fan of reggae##1
14. the person who likes lavender is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Color   | purple | aquamarine     | lavender | white | pink | amber  | emerald  |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | r&b        | classical  | soul     | rock   | jazz       | reggae   |
| Sport         | golf   | water-polo | surfing    | parkour  | tennis | volleyball | climbing |

