.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, ambient, electronic, jazz, salsa, d&b, classical
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, handball, parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, scooter, ship, train, trike
 1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the fan of classical##1
 6. the fan of funk is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the fan of funk is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person driving the trike##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
12. the person driving the bus is the fan of ambient##1
13. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of funk##1
14. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person driving the train##1
15. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | classical      | jazz     | funk  | salsa | electronic | ambient |
