 3. the person playing go is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating apricot is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is the person watching action movies##1
10. the person playing snooker is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the person playing poker##1
12. the person eating banana is the person playing bridge##1
13. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
15. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
