10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
11. the analyst is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the analyst is the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the right of the chef##1
14. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing go##1
15. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
