.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, house, metal, punk, reggae, salsa, trance
City: hamburg, hannover, nizza, edinburgh, marseilles, boston, colone
 1. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the person traveling to boston is between the fan of reggae and the fan of metal##2
 3. the fan of d&b is the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the fan of trance is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the fan of d&b is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the fan of d&b is the person traveling to hannover##1
10. the writer is the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the fan of trance is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
14. the fan of house is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dancer | photographer | musician | fisherman  | writer   | manager | coach      |
| Music-Genre   | trance | metal        | salsa    | reggae     | punk     | house   | d&b        |
| City           | hamburg   | nizza       | boston    | edinburgh | marseilles | colone   | hannover |

